Domain registration for dApps located on the IPFS network.

How does it work?

- Users go to domain name addresses .ava, .web3, .dapp, .ipfs, .defi, .gamefi;
- The extension sends a request to the Avalanche blockchain and receives an IPFS CID;
- The browser opens your decentralized application (dApp) on the IPFS network.
